<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>PixelPro Cameras - Digital Cameras & Gear</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #222; }
    header { background: #0a0a0a; color: #fff; padding: 1rem 5%; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
    nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .logo { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .logo span { color: #3b82f6; }
    nav ul { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; list-style: none; }
    nav a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
    nav a:hover { color: #3b82f6; }
    .hero { background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1510127034890-ba27508e9f1c?w=1200') center/cover; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 6rem 5% 8rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    .btn { background: #3b82f6; color: #fff; padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem; border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn:hover { background: #2563eb; }
    section { padding: 4rem 5%; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
    h2 { text-align: center; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .products { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
    .card { border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; transition: 0.2s; }
    .card:hover { box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .card img { width: 100%; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; }
    .card-body { padding: 1.5rem; }
    .card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .price { color: #3b82f6; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem; }
    .features { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; text-align: center; }
    .feature { padding: 1.5rem; }
    .feature-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .contact { background: #f9fafb; }
    .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    form input, form textarea { width: 100%; padding: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; }
    footer { background: #0a0a0a; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center; padding: 2rem 5%; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } nav ul { display: none; } .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <div class="logo">Pixel<span>Pro</span></div>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#shop">Shop</a></li>
        <li><a href="#why">Why Us</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Capture Life in Perfect Detail</h1>
    <p>Professional & beginner digital cameras, lenses, and accessories. Expert advice. Islamabad’s trusted camera store.</p>
    <a href="#shop" class="btn">Shop Cameras</a>
  </div>

  <section id="shop">
    <h2>Featured Cameras</h2>
    <div class="products">
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606983340126-99ab4feaa64a?w=600" alt="Mirrorless Camera">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>Pro Mirrorless X1</h3>
          <p>24MP, 4K 60fps, 5-axis IBIS. Perfect for creators.</p>
          <div class="price">Rs 285,000</div>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn">Inquire Now</a>
        </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502920917128-1aa500764cbd?w=600" alt="DSLR Camera">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>DSLR Master 750</h3>
          <p>32MP, Dual card slots, Weather sealed body.</p>
          <div class="price">Rs 195,000</div>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn">Inquire Now</a>
        </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581591524425-c7e0978865fc?w=600" alt="Compact Camera">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>Compact Travel Zoom</h3>
          <p>20MP, 30x optical zoom, Pocket size. For everyday shots.</p>
          <div class="price">Rs 68,000</div>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn">Inquire Now</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="why">
    <h2>Why Choose PixelPro</h2>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">📦</div>
        <h3>Official Warranty</h3>
        <p>All cameras come with 1-year local + international warranty.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">🎓</div>
        <h3>Expert Advice</h3>
        <p>Not sure what to buy? Our team shoots daily and will match you to the right gear.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">🚚</div>
        <h3>Islamabad Delivery</h3>
        <p>Free same-day delivery in Islamabad. Nationwide shipping available.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="contact">
    <h2>Visit or Message Us</h2>
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div>
        <h3>Get in Touch</h3>
        <p><strong>Address:</strong> Shop 12, Blue Area, Islamabad</p>
        <p><strong>Phone/WhatsApp:</strong> 03XX-XXXXXXX</p>
        <p><strong>Hours:</strong> Mon-Sat, 11am - 8pm</p>
        <p>We buy, sell, and trade used gear too.</p>
      </div>
      <form>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required>
        <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
        <textarea rows="4" placeholder="Which camera are you interested in?"></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="btn">Send Message</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 PixelPro Cameras. Islamabad, Pakistan. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
